lead_paragraph: Top-seeded Timea Bacsinszky of Switzerland beat fifth-seeded Timea Babos of Hungary 6-4, 7-5 on Friday to reach the Grand Prix SAR final, where she will face qualifier Marina Erakovic of New Zealand.

headline.print_headline: Top-Seeded Timea Bacsinszky Reaches Grand Prix SAR Final
headline.main: Top-Seeded Timea Bacsinszky Reaches Grand Prix SAR Final
